Class NamedSqmFunctionTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.query.sqm.produce.function.spi.AbstractSqmFunctionTemplate

        • org.hibernate.query.sqm.produce.function.spi.NamedSqmFunctionTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SelfRenderingFunctionSupport, SqmFunctionTemplate

    public class NamedSqmFunctionTemplate
extends AbstractSelfRenderingFunctionTemplate
implements SelfRenderingFunctionSupport
    Provides a standard implementation that supports the majority of the HQL functions that are translated to SQL. The Dialect and its sub-classes use this class to provide details required for processing of the associated function.
